{"tid":1463180,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"「唔好阻人啊」「無人支持啦」","createTime":"2019-08-13T12:19:21.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-13T14:30:40.000Z","uid":33587,"like":67,"dislike":35,"uniUserReply":35,"replies":[{"pid":"2b247c9cee41d20b2ddabb8d78f81e4cea12d2ef","tid":1463180,"uid":33587,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T12:19:21.000Z","msg":"屌你老母收嗲啦<br />\n琴日係搞得算係成功<br />\n有一大班人走之前仲話聽日再黎過<br />\n結果呢？<br />\n今日啲人數直線下降<br />\n冇得塞爆機場<br />\n焗住要用阻人上機嘅方法黎停止機場運作<br />\n然後有一大班撚屌上黎開po話今日有反效果 失民意之類嘅說話<br />\n原因係咩啊？<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">原因係你地呢班冚家產啊<br />\n喺屋企開po指指點點<br />\n又唔撚出黎塞</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">一隻眼黎換你地嬲一日<br />\n你地嘅憤怒會唔會過於廉價？<br />\n最大問題係你地知要點做而唔去咁做<br />\n我係政府我都笑鳩你地啦</span></span>"},{"pid":"cf2d961e7ac1526c641917e3759c0fe4a422fc0b","tid":1463180,"uid":242393,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T12:25:18.000Z","msg":"818民陣大遊行見"},{"pid":"90c8ca457cdcedd2d5d0a8da7e0982967af49877","tid":1463180,"uid":6275,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T12:25:21.000Z","msg":"停止散水分化 尊重前線手足"},{"pid":"c1079f5517566b94d7b7405c22078f5fefabacf1","tid":1463180,"uid":119173,"like":10,"dislike":2,"score":8,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T12:25:44.000Z","msg":"民意民意民意。「民意」係啲乜？<br />\n<br />\n「民意」就係Q埋雙手咩都唔使做，然後第二朝瞓醒五大訴求就達成，跟手一齊BBQ跳起大團圓結局。抗爭過程入面，最好咩都唔好煩到佢地、唔會阻到人、唔好變成滿手鮮血、要顧及型象，唔可以俾位人入。<br />\n<br />\n如果你要執著既「民意」係呢一種，咁sorry 我都係帶番個頭盔同豬咀上前線先，你繼續慢慢瞓。<br />\n但當某一日你瞓醒就話我知，我拎埋裝備帶你一齊上戰場又點話。<br />\n<br />\n我願意係你未瞓醒既時候守護住你，但都請你唔好責怪我係打生打死既時候會破壞到你型像。因為戰場上面已經得番我同你兩個人，我地無路可退。<br />\n<br />\n不割席、不分化、不篤灰。"},{"pid":"4afef07df196cd9a491df839f219896803a5d0e4","tid":1463180,"uid":33587,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"90c8ca457cdcedd2d5d0a8da7e0982967af49877","tid":1463180,"uid":6275,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T12:25:21.000Z","msg":"停止散水分化 尊重前線手足"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T12:28:01.000Z","msg":"我喺機場<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8eacd48f7c725e47fff4f086db3e4f2bfb0a5617","tid":1463180,"uid":6275,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"4afef07df196cd9a491df839f219896803a5d0e4","tid":1463180,"uid":33587,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"90c8ca457cdcedd2d5d0a8da7e0982967af49877","tid":1463180,"uid":6275,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T12:25:21.000Z","msg":"停止散水分化 尊重前線手足"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T12:28:01.000Z","msg":"我喺機場<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T12:30:10.000Z","msg":"我都喺現場 所以撐緊你啊手足"},{"pid":"ecab270710f7d18d92202f770abefcf5ef5a7999","tid":1463180,"uid":33587,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"cf2d961e7ac1526c641917e3759c0fe4a422fc0b","tid":1463180,"uid":242393,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T12:25:18.000Z","msg":"818民陣大遊行見"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T12:30:21.000Z","msg":"一直都會出<br />\n我純粹覺得喺屋企開po指指點點 只批評 不做事嘅撚屌無資格講野"},{"pid":"ab3c392c2427f3540d206d76413a00e7e439c78d","tid":1463180,"uid":115041,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T12:30:51.000Z","msg":"推！"},{"pid":"a350dafc2493c5434da351d79d26b8ade5460124","tid":1463180,"uid":270871,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T12:30:59.000Z","msg":"同意"},{"pid":"7fdd5bd37ccccca7d57af12b2c56dae56f50da8e","tid":1463180,"uid":198188,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T12:31:05.000Z","msg":"乜撚野叫和理飛丫<br />\n而家係阻人飛"},{"pid":"6ea892058b14415113a36b95ebf94bbcb1e2b358","tid":1463180,"uid":33587,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8eacd48f7c725e47fff4f086db3e4f2bfb0a5617","tid":1463180,"uid":6275,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"4afef07df196cd9a491df839f219896803a5d0e4","tid":1463180,"uid":33587,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"