兩個人，我地無路可退。<br />\n<br />\n不割席、不分化、不篤灰。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T12:44:02.000Z","msg":"同路人 互勉之"},{"pid":"ac1698b986aadcda83e240a3b9abbf168220deec","tid":1463180,"uid":270506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T12:44:18.000Z","msg":"屌你唔記得左去機場係要令外國旅客了解同支持我地，唔係阻撚住佢地要佢地難做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n而家係我地阻到外國遊客，佢地係<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">盟友</span></span>唔係敵人唔係藍屍"},{"pid":"d27e844a42e9f0c55f2b0ad7d3db5f7392948c49","tid":1463180,"uid":131122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T12:44:19.000Z","msg":"求宣傳818<br />\n無人宣傳唔會有百萬"},{"pid":"3553fe3f0b1ca0b4b47992a923fe8ea5664fdef5","tid":1463180,"uid":22436,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T12:45:05.000Z","msg":"建議前線勇武塞跑道 咪阻住和理非文宣"},{"pid":"ee4ac3e8168569cde72c896f14afd3f407c42360","tid":1463180,"uid":27664,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T12:45:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZrURqbv.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZrURqbv.png&h=829cf265&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"cc860fd4be5bfec228e27fcbbeb6a550eb654971","tid":1463180,"uid":270506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"74f0aa31680bacadf9e1d9f3264abeaeebf42c0e","tid":1463180,"uid":33587,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T12:35:31.000Z","msg":"班前線比完班客屌<br />\n仲要比你地呢班安坐家中嘅撚屌話<br />\n你地冇資格屌啊"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T12:46:30.000Z","msg":"前線唔係大曬，前線/現場有失誤但唔肯接受意見，咁同共產黨有咩分別？"},{"pid":"5b941a7ac1a935f63e8f197c451e310f9b2bbb32","tid":1463180,"uid":300758,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2b247c9cee41d20b2ddabb8d78f81e4cea12d2ef","tid":1463180,"uid":33587,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T12:19:21.000Z","msg":"屌你老母收嗲啦<br />\n琴日係搞得算係成功<br />\n有一大班人走之前仲話聽日再黎過<br />\n結果呢？<br />\n今日啲人數直線下降<br />\n冇得塞爆機場<br />\n焗住要用阻